n而家嘅採購策略係一劑一個人一個療程<br />\n要打兩劑未來先會額外採購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用依家香港嘅採購策略係唔存在<br />\n某一款疫苗要打兩劑，所以要採購幾倍劑量去完成療程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家講明1500萬支，係for 兩倍人口<br />\n佢所假設嘅接種數目係一人一劑<br />\n<br />\n所以樓上班撚樣話因為啲疫苗要打兩劑，<br />\n所以香港政府而家先要採購幾倍數量呢個論點係唔成立　<br />\n<br />\n我咪串番佢，如果真係1500萬劑，每人打兩劑<br />\n咪要混合打先夠數囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa756cf0e212ddb48fde5f3b94634e859a1c1651","tid":2322434,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcbf3b5250674097a41edcdc1eb8ade848e40ad5","tid":2322434,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a0da4086f0ee0d29ccb58fbcd366b4ff9da7fa","tid":2322434,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4178075a1f7de303f6c0d5b3392f474b4ec06d8e","tid":2322434,"uid":78039,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"你就on9，你估唔會record打咗邊隻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用下你個腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:34:23.000Z","msg":"on 9<br />\n採購以全港人口兩倍計算，<span class=\"large\">即1,500萬劑疫苗</span>，供巿民接種；若有關疫苗需要接種<span class=\"x-large\">兩劑</span>，採購量會相應<span class=\"x-large\">倍增</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/12/20201211/20201211_170633_661.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F12%2F20201211%2F20201211_170633_661.html&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=4a150198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/12/20201211/20201211_17